	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Non scripturus fueram, d. pater; proxime fueram gratias acturus pro tuis tot officiis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Sed ecce heri vesperi dicitur quidam <placeName ref="l306">Mediolano</placeName> advenisse, qui dixisse fertur <persName>Hannibalis</persName> copias omnes pessum isse, <persName>Hannibalem</persName> captum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Hodie veniunt literae d. consuli <persName ref="p8055">Ambrosio</persName> <placeName ref="l1059">Bellizona</placeName> a certo viro, in quibus nunciatur illas copias tempestate periisse et quidem in universum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Nunc, quid verum sit, audiemus brevi; existimo rem non omni carere fide.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">Addit ille in suis ad consulem literis <placeName ref="l1121">Genuenses</placeName> in maximo periculo versari, quod quidem S. Petro <persName>Corso</persName> nomine ab ipsis ad <placeName ref="l2510">Turcam</placeName> defecerit et oppidum in <placeName ref="l2801">Corsica</placeName> ceperit.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Congruunt hęc cum d. <persName ref="p8033">Bezae</persName> literis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">Addit praeterea <placeName ref="l1121">Genuenses</placeName> misisse certos homines cum mandatis <placeName ref="l306">Mediolanum</placeName>, ut ibi militem novum pararent; sed <placeName ref="l306">Mediolanensibus</placeName> militia interdictum poena capitali.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de">Doch so sygind die houptlütt und andere befelchslütt or dem verbott schon darvon gesyn.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la">Haec subito te scire volui et dubito, an sit, cui dare possim literas; existimo enim nostros iam abiisse.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vale, reverende pater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la">Calendis augusti <placeName ref="l98">Curię</placeName> anno 1564.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la">T[uus] <persName ref="p8009">F[abritius</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la">Amplissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, domino suo colendissimo.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l587">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
